947
01:11:02,939 --> 01:11:05,533
<i>Paul y el programa de Northwestern.</i>

948
01:11:06,609 --> 01:11:08,941
<i>De repente nada parecía importar.</i>

949
01:11:09,011 --> 01:11:13,004
